# Personal ops-agent job overlay drop.
#
# Files placed here (e.g. `mkt-ph-launch-monitor.md`, `flights-scan.md`)
# are dispatchable through the webhook channel exactly like the bundled
# jobs in the parent dir. The job-file resolver checks the kernel jobs
# dir first, then falls back to `_ext/`.
#
# Anything you place under `_ext/` is gitignored — see .gitignore at repo
# root and docs/architecture-public-private.md.
